 EX-BBN housemate and former Miss Tourism, Kim Chinonso Oprah, has launched her skin care line, Kims Secret. The TV reality star known to have a beautiful skin might have triggered the new adventure, wanting to share her secrets to a clear and glowing skin with fans. The products, as she has shown, are for everyone, all genders and it is equally relatively affordable. Speaking on her new business, Kim Oprah disclosed that there was need to share her daily beauty routine to the world, especially to those who have complimented her physical outlook. “I’m not an advocate of skin bleaching which has caused several skin discolorations; rather I am an advocate of usage of 100% natural,” she said.